                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2179" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0226</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8531 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“空降兵”何去何从？——HL公司顾总的挣扎与迷失</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Airborne&amp;quot;Where to go?——HL Company gu general manager of struggle and lost</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孔群喜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HL公司南京分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化；“空降兵”；文化冲突；高管团队</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enterprise culture; &amp;quot;airborne&amp;quot;; Culture conflict; Senior management team</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了HL公司南京分公司从2004年成立以来，在汽车连接器行业逐步发展壮大过程中遇到的中台企业文化冲突，以及与之相伴随的管理层迷失困境。HL公司南京分公司总经理顾总以台湾总部“空降兵”身份入主分公司，刻苦勤奋，苦心孤诣，一心想要自己的企业做大做强，奈何海峡两岸企业文化差异巨大，HL公司总部又在不够了解实际情况的背景下支持有限，以至于近年来公司业绩繁荣背后危机重重，中低层员工归属感低下，危机频现使顾总备受煎熬、素手无策。由于HL公司汽车连接器行业是典型的外资加工配套型行业，也可以说是改革开放以来驱动中国经济崛起的典型外向型制造业企业，所以如何基于中外合资企业内在特点，合理解决企业文化冲突，以提高中外合资企业资源配置优势和管理效率，不仅是具有行业特色的难题，尤其成为步入成长期的中小外向型企业进一步发展的平静。因此，作为“空降兵”的顾总和他的企业正面临着如何纠正用人观念、融合企业文化以及变革管理模式的巨大挑战。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes that the HL company gradually encountered Mainland and Taiwan enterprise culture conflict, and accompanied by management dilemma gradually in the process of development in the automotive connector industry since it was established in 2004, Nanjing branch. GU manager of Nanjing branch company of HL As a Taiwan headquarters &quot;airborne&quot; into the branch industrious, to their own enterprises bigger and stronger,but as the corporate culture varies across the Taiwan straits, corporate headquarters and HL in not enough to understand the actual situation under the background of limited support, so that the company&#39;s performance in recent years behind the prosperity crisis, lower-level employees in low sense of belonging, crisis appear frequently makes GU total suffering, without doing. As for the HL company car connector industry is a type of Foreign processing industry supporting or A typical export-oriented manufacturing enterprises  driving China&#39;s economic rise since the reform and opening up of a typical export-oriented manufacturing enterprises, so how reasonable to solve the enterprise culture conflict,based on sino-foreign joint venture enterprise inner characteristics a joint venture in order to improve the allocation of resources advantage and the management efficiency, is not only a problem with industry characteristics, but also the bottleneck to the further development of small and medium-sized export-oriented enterprise growth . As &quot;airborne&quot; GU and his enterprise are faced with the great challenge of change management of how to correct the Concept of choose and employ persons idea, the fusion of choose and employ persons the enterprise culture and. Change management mode.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化建设 外向型企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
